    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require CCTV in all neonatal and paediatric areas in hospitals",
        "additional_details": "Following recent events covered widely by the media, it is reasonable to ask our government to consider the use of CCTV within our neonatal and paediatric units within hospitals. To be considered as a means of safeguarding vulnerable babies or children from preventable harm or abuse.",
        "background": "We want the Government to require hospitals to implement CCTV within our neonatal and paediatric units to help safeguard vulnerable babies or children from preventable harm or abuse.",
